ide parade and tom harkin was its grand marshal he was also the grand marshal for the chicago disability pride parade that same year published worksedit harkin tom and thomas c e five minutes to midnight why the nuclear threat is growing faster than ever carol publishing corporation  isbn  see alsoedit united states navy portal st century democrats referencesedit  beaumont thomas apnewsbreak harkin wont seek th senate term bigstoryaporg retrieved    mccrone william p  senator tom harkin reflections on disability policy  journal of rehabilitation  find articles at bnet findarticlescom retrieved    biography of tom harkin harkinsenategov retrieved    judith miller  tom harkins oldtime religion  biography new york times magazine retrieved    miller judith tom harkins oldtime religion the new york times february   accessed november   after his mother died harkin an altar boy went to dowling catholic high school in des moines and won a navy rotc scholarship to college  politicocom videos linkbrightcovecom retrieved    budiansky s july   cures or quackery us news  world reports archived from the original on september   retrieved    senator tom harkin disappointed that nccam hasnt validated more cam sciencebased medicine retrieved    s   all actions united states congress retrieved  january    s   cbo congressional budget office retrieved  january    bradford hazel  january  senate passes pension relief for charities rural cooperatives pensions and investments retrieved  january    s   all actions united states congress retrieved  april    s   summary united states congress retrieved  april    sink justin  april  obama congress has clear choice on minimum wage the hill retrieved  april    bolton alexander  april  reid punts on minimumwage hike the hill retrieved  april    bolton alexander  april  centrist republicans cool to minimum wage hike compromise the hill retrieved  april    a b ability magazine senator harkin  updating the ada  retrieved    ability magazine senator