ns in april  leading their washington dc office in  mrs harkin became a director of conocophillips mrs harkin currently sits on the iowa board of regents the body responsible for overseeing the states public universities senator harkin made a brief cameo appearance as himself in the political satire dave  as did his fellow senators christopher dodd howard metzenbaum paul simon and alan k simpson the harkins daughter amy appeared on the nbc daytime reality series starting over from  to  although tom harkin never appeared on the show his voice was heard when his daughter spoke to him on the phone she is currently a graduate student at the ucla anderson school of management in  new york city held its first disability pride parade and tom harkin was its grand marshal he was also the grand marshal for the chicago disability pride parade that same year published worksedit harkin tom and thomas c e five minutes to midnight why the nuclear threat is growing faster than ever carol publishing corporation  isbn  see alsoedit united states navy portal st century democrats referencesedit  beaumont thomas apnewsbreak harkin wont seek th senate term bigstoryaporg retrieved    mccrone william p  senator tom harkin reflections on disability policy  journal of rehabilitation  find articles at bnet findarticlescom retrieved    biography of tom harkin harkinsenategov retrieved    judith miller  tom harkins oldtime religion  biography new york times magazine retrieved    miller judith tom harkins oldtime religion the new york times february   accessed november   after his mother died harkin an altar boy went to dowling catholic high school in des moines and won a navy rotc scholarship to college  politicocom videos linkbrightcovecom retrieved    budiansky s july   cures or quackery us news  world reports archived from the original on september   retrieved    senator tom harkin disappointed that nccam hasnt validated more cam sciencebased medicine retrieved    s   all actions united stat